{
  "id": "adv_event_2311_01_05",
  "title": "三人でなら\nどこまでも",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブバトルが終わって、一週間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "— A week after the live battle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1900
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ～\nここが今日泊まる温泉旅館なんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa~\nThis is the hot spring ryokan we’re staying at today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9000000555,
      "endTime": 9.233333333300001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "トップ5に勝ったお祝いに温泉旅行をプレゼントなんて\n{user}さんも太っ腹やなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To give us a hot spring trip as a celebration for beating a top 5 idol…\n{user}-san is so generous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.524149664,
      "endTime": 17.1797280865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.3797281819
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "私の地元の山形に三人で旅行出来るなんて最高だよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the best that we can travel to my hometown Yamagata together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3797281819,
      "endTime": 23.376032026399997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.5826985596
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。たまにはこういうのも悪くないわ\n今日はゆっくり羽を伸ばしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true. It’s not bad to do this once in a while.\nLet’s relax and unwind today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5826985596,
      "endTime": 30.7043991326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.9043990372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ほな瑠依ちゃん、さっそく露天風呂に行くで～\nすべすべの背中、うちがしっかり洗わせてもらいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ Rui-chan‚ I’m going to the open-air bath first~\nI’ll make sure to wash your smooth back nice and clean!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9043990372,
      "endTime": 39.1782764672,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.3716097433
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか急に目の色が変わった気がするけど……\nじゃあ、温泉に入って日頃の疲れを癒しましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like your eyes suddenly changed color…\nWell then‚ shall we go to the hot spring and relieve our fatigue?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3716097433,
      "endTime": 47.7320860464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.865419205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、いいお湯だったね～\n体がぽっかぽかだよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh That felt good\nI feel so warm and relaxed~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8654163916,
      "endTime": 56.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "温泉の後はお楽しみの夕食や\nテーブルにご馳走が用意してあるで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the hot spring‚ it’s time for a happy dinner.\nThe feast is ready at the table.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.8868173044,
      "endTime": 63.3496290604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.5562957843
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、まさか鍋料理が出るとは思わなかったわね\n旅館で鍋ってめずらしいんじゃないかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I didn’t expect to have hot pot.\nIsn’t it rare to have hot pot at a ryokan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5562957843,
      "endTime": 70.6162960132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.8029625655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "宿を予約する時に{user}さんが\n「夕食は鍋料理でお願いします」って頼んだらしいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san asked for\n“hot pot for dinner‚ please” when he made the reservation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8029625655,
      "endTime": 78.5482688665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "さすが、うちらのことよう分かってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected‚ he knows us well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7416019519,
      "endTime": 81.90659051729999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.1199238698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの打ち上げといえば鍋だよねっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of TRINITYAiLE celebrations‚ it’s gotta be hot pot!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.1199238698,
      "endTime": 85.46666666670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.7412579776
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そうね。さっそくいただきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ that’s right. Let’s dig in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7412579776,
      "endTime": 89.5162693263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "いただきまーす！　あむっ、もぐもぐ……\nう～ん！　美味しい～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for the food! Ah~‚ munch‚ munch…\nMmm! Delicious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.8229343813,
      "endTime": 98.0719819468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.8229343813
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.2719821375
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "こんな風に旅先で食べるお鍋も悪くないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not bad to have hot pot like this while traveling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2719821375,
      "endTime": 102.4719822329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.7053151053
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "これからライブで遠征した時は、打ち上げで\n全国のご当地鍋を食べるのもいいかもしれへんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe we should have local hot pot for our celebration\nwhen we’re on tour for live performances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7053151053,
      "endTime": 109.9148614806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "それいいね！　三人でいろんなお鍋を食べてみたい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a great idea! I want to try all sorts of hot pot with you two!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1015280328,
      "endTime": 115.0494643769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.2561309101
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "ライブで全国を回る……いいかもしれないわね\nいろんな変わったお鍋が食べられそうだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Touring the country for lives… That might be nice.\nWe could eat all kinds of unique hot pots.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2561309101,
      "endTime": 122.62960007209999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.8296001675
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "変わった鍋といえば、関西には砂糖のかわりに\n綿菓子を入れる鍋料理があるらしいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of unique hot pots‚ I heard there’s a hot pot dish in Kansai\nwhere they use cotton candy instead of sugar.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.8296001675,
      "endTime": 130.06606256979998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.2793957314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "甘い綿飴がお肉と絡んで美味しいらしいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apparently‚ the sweet cotton candy goes well with the meat and it’s delicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.2793957314,
      "endTime": 134.6054277024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.8120942833
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "お鍋に甘いお菓子を入れるなんて興味深いわね\n私もやってみようかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Putting sweet candy in hot pot… That’s interesting.\nI wonder if I should try it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8120942833,
      "endTime": 141.5320943596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_05-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど、甘いグミを持って来てるからこのお鍋に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just so happen to have some gummies… I’ll put them in this hot pot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.7187610072,
      "endTime": 145.59999847409998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
